Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: My Hammock Spot
Description: A small eucalytpus grove on the edge of Isla Vista. I spend my down time here swinging in a hammock. A little patch of trees perfect to watch the sunsets.
InfoURL: There is no real name for this location but all the students know about it :))

Name: Emerald Bay State Park Lookout
Description: An overlook of South Lake Tahoe. Area filled with rocks and trees. This photo is of my grandmother on our Thanksgiving Trip years ago.

Name: Lake Cachuma Santa Barbara
Description: Lake Cahuma is a good sized lake surrounded by trees as well as good trail heads. The photo I took of my friends sitting upon an abondonded dome of some kind.

Name: Santa Barbara County Clerk - Recorder Office
Description: The Santa Barbara County Clerk office is an older and historic building in SB county. With its adobe walls the history of SB is kept. Overlooking the ocean as well as downtown SB it is an popular tourist attraction as well as a perfect location for a day trip with friends !

Name: My Childhood Home !
Description: This backyard of my family home is what has kept my family and I sane during the pandemic. We have been able to enjoy and work with the land and our animals. We raise 4 doggos here! We have olive, grapefruit, lemon, orange, and apricot trees ! As well as eucalyptus !
InfoURL: There is no real URL, this is my childhood home :)
